                <p style="text-align: center;">  Did you know that one-fourth of the world’s starving population lives in India – that is three times the population of France!</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">  The first step to solving a social issue is to understand it. </p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">  We FoodCare invites you to be a part of our effort to understand the reality of malnutrition in India and discuss ways you and we can be part of the solution.</p>
