            <p style="text-align: center;">Everyone should follow proper food hygiene and quality checks at the point of collection, transportation and distribution of fresh or surplus cooked food. </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Ensure about expiry products are not expired before collecting them from donors</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Once you reach the feed spot (slum areas) - take a pause, meet the beneficiaries, speak with them, give them the food. Be compassionate, kind and respectful</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Before you set out for the donation drive take a picture with the Food Donor. </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Take pictures with the beneficiaries, but first, ask them if they are comfortable with being photographed. </p>
